    <body>
        <p>You can create checklist templates to save time when adding new checklists. When you create a new checklist, you can base it on any of your saved templates. This is quite useful when you are creating many checklists that share the same type, description, columns, rows, or notes. Rather than typing all the information manually, the template populates the relevant fields automatically.</p>
